description.narrative: Government of Tanzania completed a comprehensive Education Sector Analysis providing a strong evidence base for the preparation of the new Education Sector Development Plan 2021/2022-2025/2026 and strategic priorities to address the areas of deprivation in the fulfilment of the rights of education to all Tanzanian children. Additionally, a newly Developed ;School Based Assessment System is set to strengthen teacher’s capacity to formatively assess learning outcomes during children’s learning, empowering the teachers to take appropriate corrective actions in the classrooms and provide feedback to children. | Status:Met | As-of Date:20/12/2021
